lead_paragraph: Sri Lanka suffered another injury setback ahead of the second test against Australia in Galle with seamer Nuwan Pradeep suffering a hamstring strain during practice, a cricket board official said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Sri Lanka's Pradeep Doubtful for Galle Test
